01/07/2005
TIRANA, Albania -- German Ambassador to Tirana Hans Peter Annen signed an agreement with defence ministry officials Thursday (30 June) on the donation of 12 helicopters to the Albanian Army. 
The initiative was part of a visit by a delegation from the European Aeronautic Defence and Space Company (EADS). 
Annen said the helicopters would help modernise the army in accordance with NATO standards. 
(Albanian News - 01/07/05)
